{
  "text": "The European Holocaust Research Infrastructure (EHRI) project aims to assist the process of conducting transnational and comparative studies of the Holocaust by bringing together in an online portal (https: //portal.ehri-project.eu/) archival material across a geographically dispersed and fragmented archival landscape [CITATION_1] . Its principle goal is related to data collection, integration, and curation.",
